text.tspan: Goals & Needs
Everyday Activities
Motivations
Stefan is a very inquisitive person, so he needs to
access as much information as possible.
He has never been tattooed, so he needs the ability
to view a variety of artwork.
Stefan loves reading and giving reviews. He needs
to be able to access customer feedback and gain
tattoo maintenance information.
He is always on his phone, so a functional app
would be ideal for him to research ideas and
artists.
Stefan is a gym rat. He works out twice a day.
(Monday- Saturday)
Posts pictures on his IG showing his brand at
least one time per day.
Works from home, but travels frequently to
meet with potential buyers.
Schedules weekly meetings with his business
partners.
Hikes every weekend.
Stefan is motivated by personal goals. He is
extremely strict with his time.
He would love to finally go through with the
tattoo process to showcase on IG and other
social media handles.
His outdoor sporting brand Archer is his driving
force!!!
Anything dealing with outdoors he is all for it!
Frustrations
Stefan’s Direct Quotes
Stefan is very passionate, so when he feels like
his ideas are not heard he becomes irritated.
He is a very busy person, so he needs to have
the ability to quickly find what he is looking for
or else he will interest.
“I think I am ready for my first tattoo. I am
nervous, but also super stoked!”
“I would love to be branded with my brand’s
logo!”
“Does it hurt that badly?”
Device & Internet Usage
Stefan Markovich
“ The Outdoorsman”
Stefan is a 29-year-old adrenaline junky!
He’s an entrepreneur and currently lives
in Phoenix, AZ.
Stefan is fully focused on creating and
launching his outdoor sporting brand. He
utilizes Social Media on a daily basis to
highlight his brand and showcase his
apparel line. He is impassioned by sports
and would live outdoors if he could. He is
the most comfortable shirtless.
Stefan is a very sociable person but is
ok with being alone. He really enjoys
his alone time.
